        role = "cre"))
Description: An 'RStudio' addin to visualize time series. Time series are searched in the global environment as data.frame objects with a column of type date and a column of type numberic. Interactive charts are produced using 'plotly' package.
URL: https://github.com/donlelef/tsviz
